videos.headline: Baylor's Carrington scores from the wide-open lane
videos.description: Baylor's DiJonai Carrington takes advantage of an open path to the basket for a score.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Baylor's Carrington scores from the wide-open lane) 2021/03/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: NaLyssa Smith goes behind the back, drops beautiful dime for Baylor
videos.description: Baylor's NaLyssa Smith dribbles behind her back for an impressive assist to Caitlin Bickle for a bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (NaLyssa Smith goes behind the back, drops beautiful dime for Baylor) 2021/03/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Michigan's Hillmon muscles for bucket after grabbing her own rebound
videos.description: Michigan's Naz Hillmon grabs an offensive rebound off her own miss and fights for a tough bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Michigan's Hillmon muscles for bucket after grabbing her own rebound) 2021/03/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Carrington comes up with clutch steal, and-1 for Baylor
videos.description: Baylor's DiJonai Carrington grabs a steal on the defensive end and takes it all the way for the and-1 bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Carrington comes up with clutch steal, and-1 for Baylor) 2021/03/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Michigan forces OT vs. Baylor with Hillmon's bucket
videos.description: Michigan's Naz Hillmon scores the game-tying bucket as the Wolverines head to overtime vs. Baylor.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Michigan forces OT vs. Baylor with Hillmon's bucket) 2021/03/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor escapes vs. Michigan in OT to advance to Elite Eight
videos.description: Michigan puts up a last-second 3-pointer to try to force double overtime, but it doesn't drop and Baylor defeats the Wolverines 78-75 to advance to the Elite Eight.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Baylor escapes vs. Michigan in OT to advance to Elite Eight) 2021/03/27 ESHEET
